---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About">
  <h1 class="text-[28px] font-bold font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-heading mb-6">
    About Tidox Hub
  </h1>

  <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-near-black mb-4">
    Tidox Learning Hub is an automated daily intelligence brief — curated and narrated by AI, built by a solo developer. Each morning, a personalized digest of trending topics, analysis, and insights lands in your inbox, complete with a narrated video version.
  </p>

  <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-near-black mb-4">
    Every day, the pipeline scrapes trending topics, generates insights, produces a narrated video brief, and publishes it here. It's a fully automated system that runs on a schedule, bringing you the most relevant information without the noise.
  </p>

  <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-near-black mb-4">
    Built by Tido Emanuele. This is an experiment in what one developer + AI can ship — exploring the intersection of automation, personalization, and accessibility in digital content.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8">
    <a href="https://github.com/tidoemanuele" class="text-terracotta hover:underline">GitHub</a>
  </div>
</Base>
